## 15. Create EF Migration and update database

Run from the server project directory (`ShipmentTracker/ShipmentTracker`):
```bash
cd /tmp/sv-3993fbc230314d819643313ae54f5003/ShipmentTracker/ShipmentTracker
dotnet ef migrations add AddShipments -- --environment Development
```

If `dotnet ef` is not available, install it first:
```bash
dotnet tool install --global dotnet-ef
```

If migration fails because of existing migrations that don't include the new Shipment entity, just remove the Migrations folder and recreate:
```bash
rm -rf Data/Migrations
dotnet ef migrations add InitialCreate -- --environment Development
```

